PROJECT SUMMARY

This is a Gen-AI powered Travel Planner + Travel Assistant mobile application.

A user can:

Ask for a trip plan

Ask travel questions

Ask for hotels, restaurants, attractions, ticket prices

Ask for estimated trip cost

Ask for nearby areas to explore

Use a chat assistant for follow-up queries

The system will:

ONLY answer travel-related questions

ALWAYS output structured travel information

NEVER handle non-travel queries

Provide itinerary, cost, hotels, restaurants, nearby places, taxi prices

Use CSV data for 5 cities + LLM for everything else
